benak.tomas.crimemonitor.library

Class CrimeSummaryWithUtvarBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • benak.tomas.crimemonitor.library.CrimeSummaryWithUtvarBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UtvarBasedCrimeSummary, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CrimeSummaryWithUtvarAndIntervalBase, UtvarKodANazev

    public class CrimeSummaryWithUtvarBase
extends java.lang.Object
implements UtvarBasedCrimeSummary, java.io.Serializable
    A base class associating the contained crime statistics with a particular police department and code.

    This is just a base class, containing no crime statistics, only the police department data. It acts as a logical abstract base class for other classes that need to associate their crime statistics with a police department.

    Author:
    Tom
